dct_title_s: Map of Property of the Passaic Park Company, Passaic Park, opposite Passaic City, N.J.
dct_description_sm: Map shows blocks A-Z divided into lots. Streets are labeled and lot dimensions are given. The map is an advertisement for an auction held Friday and Saturday, July 4 and 5th, 1890. Map also provides additional contact information.
